---
// src/pages/projects/health-tracking.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Health Analytics Ecosystem | Ean Cummings">
  <article class="project-deep-dive animate-fade-in">
    
    <!-- ==================== 1. CINEMATIC HEADER ==================== -->
    <header class="project-hero">
      <div class="project-hero-container">
        <span class="pro-tag-badge">Active Production Sprint</span>
        <h1 class="pro-headline">Healthur Ecosystem</h1>
        <p class="pro-subheading">
          A native iOS health architecture bridging high-frequency biometric streaming with on-device LLM inference to provide context-aware recovery coaching.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
    </header>

    <!-- ==================== 2. ARCHITECTURE BLOCK ==================== -->
    <section class="pro-content-row">
      <div class="pro-sidebar">
        <span class="row-num">01 / Scope</span>
        <h2>System Architecture Objectives</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pro-main-body">
        <p>
          Healthur is designed to solve the data-overload problem inherent in modern wearables. By leveraging <strong>Apple HealthKit</strong>, the system aggregates disparate data streams—HRV, sleep stages, resting heart rate, and training load—into a unified, user-centered Smart Health Score.
        </p>
        <p>
          The architecture is built on a privacy-first, on-device processing model. By utilizing <strong>CoreML and iOS 26 integrated LLM frameworks</strong>, the system performs all personalized health inference locally, eliminating the need for sensitive physiological data to ever leave the user's encrypted device storage.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ==================== 3. DATA TOPOLOGY BLOCK ==================== -->
    <section class="pro-content-row">
      <div class="pro-sidebar">
        <span class="row-num">02 / Infrastructure</span>
        <h2>Data Pipeline & AI Integration</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pro-main-body">
        <p>
          The system pipeline treats biometric data as a multi-signal control loop. I am currently architecting the <strong>InsightEngine</strong>, which correlates daily recovery metrics with user-logged qualitative reflections to detect patterns that simple numeric charting misses.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Text-Based Topology Table replacing the image -->
        <div class="topology-specs-box">
          <div class="topo-row">
            <span class="topo-label">UI Layer</span>
            <span class="topo-value">SwiftUI Screens (Home, Activity, Recovery, Insights)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="topo-row">
            <span class="topo-label">Logic Layer</span>
            <span class="topo-value">MVVM Architecture isolating ViewModels from raw data logic</span>
          </div>
          <div class="topo-row">
            <span class="topo-label">Data Managers</span>
            <span class="topo-value">Apple HealthKit integrations for Workout, Sleep, and HRV models</span>
          </div>
          <div class="topo-row">
            <span class="topo-label">AI Engine</span>
            <span class="topo-value">On-Device LLM managing the InsightEngine and PlanBuilderAI</span>
          </div>
          <div class="topo-row">
            <span class="topo-label">Core Security</span>
            <span class="topo-value">CryptoKit encryption and iCloud Keychain passkey authentication</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ==================== 4. TECH SPECS DASHBOARD ==================== -->
    <section class="pro-content-row border-top-only">
      <div class="pro-sidebar">
        <span class="row-num">03 / Tech Stack</span>
        <h2>Development Tools</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pro-main-body">
        <div class="specs-mini-grid">
          <div class="spec-mini-card">
            <h4>Languages</h4>
            <p>Swift / SwiftUI / Combine Framework</p>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-mini-card">
            <h4>Biometric Source</h4>
            <p>Apple HealthKit & CoreBluetooth</p>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-mini-card">
            <h4>AI Engine</h4>
            <p>CoreML & On-Device Apple LLM</p>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-mini-card">
            <h4>Data Security</h4>
            <p>CryptoKit & Passkey Authentication</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </article>
</Layout>

<!-- ==================== STYLES ==================== -->
<style>
  .project-deep-dive {
    max-width: 1024px;
    width: min(100%, 92%);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  /* --- Hero Styling --- */
  .project-hero {
    min-height: 45vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .project-hero-container {
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .pro-tag-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    background: rgba(47, 128, 237, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(47, 128, 237, 0.2);
    border-radius: 100px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .pro-headline {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    color: var(--text-apple);
  }

  .pro-subheading {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 650px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .grid-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 32px 32px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* --- Row Layout Mechanics --- */
  .pro-content-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 64px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .border-top-only {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pro-content-row {
      grid-template-columns: 3fr 5fr;
      gap: 64px;
    }
    .pro-sidebar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 100px;
    }
  }

  .row-num {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .pro-sidebar h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-top: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .pro-main-body {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .pro-main-body p {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* --- Topology Table (Replaces Images) --- */
  .topology-specs-box {
    margin-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-top: 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .topo-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .topo-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .topo-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .topo-value {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 300;
    text-align: right;
    flex: 2;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .topo-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .topo-value {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  /* --- Technical Spec Breakdown --- */
  .specs-mini-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .spec-mini-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .spec-mini-card h4 {
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .spec-mini-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
</style>